パッケージ org.interledger.codecs.oer

  • クラスのサマリー 
    クラス 説明
    OerGeneralizedTimeCodec
    An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER GeneralizedTime.
    OerGeneralizedTimeCodec.OerGeneralizedTime
    A typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type, in this case ZonedDateTime.
    OerIA5StringCodec
    An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER IA5String.
    OerIA5StringCodec.OerIA5String
    A typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type (in this case, String).
    OerLengthPrefixCodec
    An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER Length prefix octets.
    OerLengthPrefixCodec.OerLengthPrefix
    An typing mechanism for registering codecs for length prefixes (as opposed to normal integer types).
    OerOctetStringCodec
    An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER OctetString.
    OerOctetStringCodec.OerOctetString
    A typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type (in this case, byte[]).
    OerSequenceOfAddressCodec
    A sequence-of type is encoded as a quantity field followed by the encoding of each occurrence of the repeating field of the sequence-of type (zero or more).
    OerSequenceOfAddressCodec.OerSequenceOfAddress
    An typing mechanism for registering codecs.
    OerUint256Codec
    An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER 256-Bit integer type as defined by the Interledger ASN.1 definitions.
    OerUint256Codec.OerUint256
    Merely a typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type.
    OerUint32Codec
    An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER 32-Bit integer type as defined by the Interledger ASN.1 definitions.
    OerUint32Codec.OerUint32
    Merely a typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type.
    OerUint64Codec
    An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER 64-Bit unsigned integer type as defined by the Interledger ASN.1 definitions.
    OerUint64Codec.OerUint64
    Merely a typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type.
    OerUint8Codec
    An extension of Codec for reading and writing an ASN.1 OER 8-Bit integer type as defined by the Interledger ASN.1 definitions.
    OerUint8Codec.OerUint8
    Merely a typing mechanism for registering multiple codecs that operate on the same type.
